'''戴维阁皇宫'''（Devi Garh Palace）是[[印度|印度]]的一所皇宫酒店，位于[[拉贾斯坦邦|拉贾斯坦邦]][[乌代布尔|乌代布尔]]东北方28公里的一座18世纪皇宫<ref name=nyt>[http://travel.nytimes.com/travel/guides/asia/india/rajasthan/udaipur/49030/devi-garh/hotel-detail.html New York Times Review - Devi Garh] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110811151254/http://travel.nytimes.com/travel/guides/asia/india/rajasthan/udaipur/49030/devi-garh/hotel-detail.html |date=2011-08-11 }} [[New_York_Times|New York Times]].</ref><ref>[http://books.google.com/books?id=5JoGt4pz-rIC&pg=PA164&dq=devi+garh&lr=&as_brr=0#PPA164,M1 Arabian Nights] ''The Dragon's Playground: Exploring Asia with Panache'', by Christine Meaney, Various. Published by PPP Company Ltd, 2005. ISBN 988-98225-7-1. ''Page 164''.</ref>。

2006年，《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》称之为印度最豪华的顶级酒店之一<ref>[http://travel.nytimes.com/frommers/travel/guides/asia/india/rajasthan/frm_rajasthan_3509010002.html?pagewanted=print Devi Garh, one of India's top hotels.] [[New_York_Times|New York Times]], November 20, 2006.</ref>，[[弗罗默旅行指南|弗罗默旅行指南]]称之为“次大陆最佳酒店”，“不只是美丽，更是惊艳。”<ref name=nyt/> 2008年，Discovery Travel and Living系列列出55座五大洲的梦幻酒店，而印度仅有的另两座酒店就是[[乌代布尔|乌代布尔]]的[[湖之宫殿|湖之宫殿]]和[[斋浦尔|斋浦尔]]的[[伦巴宫殿|伦巴宫殿]]<ref>[http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/News_by_Industry/Discovery_brings_home_Dream_Hotels/articleshow/3361483.cms Discovery brings home global Dream Hotels from Aug 21] {{Wayback|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/News_by_Industry/Discovery_brings_home_Dream_Hotels/articleshow/3361483.cms |date=20180907145950 }} [[The_Economic_Times|The Economic Times]], Aug 13, 2008.</ref>。

